item.title: On Thursday: Open Hadoop User Group Munich
item.description: On Thursday: Open Hadoop User Group Munich # If one evening of Apache Hadoop is not enough for you: The next Christmas Meetup in Germany takes place one day later in Munich. <li When: Thursday December 17, 2009 at 5:30pm open end Where: eCircle AG, Nymphenburger Straße 86, 80636 München (“Bruckmann” Building, “U1 Mailinger Str”, map in German http://www.ecircle.com/de/kontakt/anfahrt.html and look for the signs) Talks scheduled by Bob and Lars:
